ている神父からウィステリアの買い手が決まったと告げられて……。\r\n\r\n脚本：山下憲一\r\n絵コンテ：山本靖貴\r\n演出：山本靖貴\r\n総作画監督：大沢美奈"},{"id":1156431,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1156431","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"邂逅","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2023-01-15","comment":3,"desc":"悪魔が視える目を対価とし、マルバスと一緒に生きていく契約をしたウィステリア。マルバスが昔、対価として受け取った家で暮らし始めた２人だが、目の見えないウィステリアには家事全般は難しかった。さらに、人間が生きていくためには食事などが必要であることを改めて知ったマルバスは街へ。ついでに寄った高級ブティックでウィステリアは伯爵ブラックベル家のダイアナと出逢う。同世代の２人は意気投合し、一緒に買い物を始める。\r\n\r\n脚本：山下憲一　絵コンテ：白田小介　演出：陳暁燦　総作画監督：鈴木光"},{"id":1156432,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1156432","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2023-01-22","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1156433,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1156433","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2023-01-29","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1156434,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1156434","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2023-02-05","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1156435,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1156435","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2023-02-12","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1156436,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1156436","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2023-02-19","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1156437,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1156437","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2023-02-26","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1156438,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1156438","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2023-03-05","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1156439,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1156439","type":0,"sort":10,"name":"","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2023-03-12","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1156440,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1156440","type":0,"sort":11,"name":"","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2023-03-19","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1156441,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1156441","type":0,"sort":12,"name":"","duration":"00:23:40","airdate":"2023-03-26","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":1157044,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1157044","type":0,"sort":13,"name":"","duration":"00:2